Title: AN ACT TO AMEND CONMMONWEALTH ACT NUMBERED SIXTY-SEVEN ENTITLED "AN ACT MAKING APPROPRIATIONS FOR PUBLIC WORKS", AS AMENDED BY COMMONWEALTH ACT NUMBERED THREE HUNDRED TWENTY-EIGHT.(awÞhi(
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 377, August 23, 1938 ]
AN ACT TO AMEND CONMMONWEALTH ACT NUMBERED SIXTY-SEVEN ENTITLED "AN ACT MAKING APPROPRIATIONS FOR PUBLIC WORKS", AS AMENDED BY COMMONWEALTH ACT NUMBERED THREE HUNDRED TWENTY-EIGHT.(awÞhi(
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The following items under section one, paragraph (d), subsection A of Commonwealth Act Numbered Sixty-seven, as amended, are further amended so as to read as follows:


BATANGAS


"26. For an additional room for the San Jose Central School 
₱2,000.00


"TAYABAS


"13. For the Maka barrio school, Lucban"
1,500.00"


Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved, August 23, 1938.
